Class SequentialRobustRangingAndRssiPositionEstimator3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.position.SequentialRobustRangingAndRssiPositionEstimator<com.irurueta.geometry.Point3D>
      • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.position.SequentialRobustRangingAndRssiPositionEstimator3D
  • public class SequentialRobustRangingAndRssiPositionEstimator3D
extends SequentialRobustRangingAndRssiPositionEstimator<com.irurueta.geometry.Point3D>
    Robustly estimates 3D position, using RSSI readings first to obtain an initial coarse position estimation, and then ranging readings to refine such estimation.
